high_descs: Walk straight to the toilet, turn left, walk a few steps, turn right towards the tub, and then turn left to face the bathroom counter.
Take the towel from the circle holder on the wall.
Turn around to face the bath tub.
Place the towel in the tub.
Take a few steps straight, turn right, and walk towards the sink.
Take the towel from the ring holder on the wall to the right of the sink.
Turn around and head towards the tub.
Place the towel in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place the two towels from the towel holders in to the tub.

high_descs: Walk up to the toilet, then turn left and walk over to the sink counter.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal ring on the wall to your right.
Take a step forward, then turn around and look down.
Put the was cloth in the tub.
Walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the wash cloth off of the metal right on the wall to the right of the mirror.
Turn around and walk over to the tub.
Put the wash cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths into the tub.
